      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything feels so pointless lately. i look at the news and the climate stuff and it just feels like we're all just watching the clock tick down on a dead planet. how are you even supposed to care about a future that isn't even going to happen? it feels like we're all just staying for a funeral.",
