      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"nobody will notice\" part is what gets me. It makes everything feel so hollow. If the whole world is just a sinking ship, then what's the point of even trying to stay on board? It feels like the most logical thing would be to just stop fighting it and leave early so you don't have to watch the end.",
